[resource]
script = ExtResource("1_ieb33")
release_version = "v1.2.6"
notes = "[TITLE]One Year Later
Happy birthday, Toontown: The Grindworks!
[TITLE]Engine
Updated to Godot version 4.6.1
Swapped to rendering with DirectX on Windows
  If you were unable to launch older versions of the game on a Windows device, this may have resolved your issue
[TITLE]Game
Runs now have scores
  Your highest score will be tracked in the Statistics menu
Added a win screen to the end of the game
[TITLE]Items
Added Rainbow Jellybean (5-Star) (Locked)
Monocle no longer shows detailed item descriptions
  Item descriptions can now be toggled on/off via the settings menu
Wingtips now additionally grant +10% Speed
Renamed BIG Foghorn to Silver Foghorn
[TITLE]Tweaks
Added buttons to visit game resources on the Title Screen
The \"Skip Intro\" button in settings will no longer hide if you haven't completed your first run, but will be disabled until you do
You can now disable the item pickup notification in settings
Slightly modified the achievement notification animation
[TITLE]Cog Creator
The Cog Creator can now import and edit Cogs stored in subdirectories under the custom_cogs folder
[TITLE]Bugfixes
Fixed an issue where Gag Vouchers would be displayed out of order on the item panel upon reloading a saved game
Fixed an issue with one of The Stranger's sound effects
Addressed some minor collision issues
Added Navigation Regions for the Doodle in some rooms where they were not present before
Minor text fixes
[TITLE]For Modders
Added in the back-end for a canceled expansion to gags, includes:
  The ability to swap out individual gags for new ones
  Gag Shops that roll and offer random \"alt gags\" for the player to choose
  Some miscellaneous additions to gag scripts (Throw gags now have the optional ability to apply status effects)
[TITLE]Hotfix #1
Fixed a regression in Lure's damage/accuracy nerf values
Fixed the Gag Panel on the pause menu not responding to player input
[TITLE]Hotfix #2
The win screen will now display your Toon's name
Rainbow Jellybean will no longer allow Professor Pete to gain infinite jellybeans
Cash Register will also now refresh the battle UI to reflect your current bean balance as Professor Pete
Fixed a mishap that occurred when White-Out spawned secret floors
Fixed a Mole Stomp game that did not charge your Pocket Prank upon victory
Shoes will now show their taglines in the Stranger Shop
Modders: The Gag Shop is now properly functional. Rejoice!"
metadata/_custom_type_script = "uid://d1j0hh6tsgy0r"
